The installation can fail due to a known problem with RcppArmadillo and Mac.
The error message that I had is: "ld: library not found for -lgfortran".
Please refer to the following website which provides a comprehensive solution:

https://thecoatlessprofessor.com/programming/rcpp-rcpparmadillo-and-os-x-mavericks--lgfortran-and--lquadmath-error/
